{"tid":2284251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星火洗錢指控無下文 販毒男囚42月","createTime":"2020-11-13T06:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T11:15:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"238b9d3b3a8d2a44e09631cf27e180b60d19396e","tid":2284251,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/33JOH77ZUBCBFLB6CQQ2AE2DAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F33JOH77ZUBCBFLB6CQQ2AE2DAU%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=a1858eb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F33JOH77ZUBCBFLB6CQQ2AE2DAU%2F&h=c87bc57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/33JOH77ZUBCBFLB6CQQ2AE2DAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n星火洗錢指控無下文 販毒男囚42月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GLe1Tb9SyiRBjyYC1hSS99C1guE=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V3COGTAYANAZ7BROXSLPV4QD3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGLe1Tb9SyiRBjyYC1hSS99C1guE%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV3COGTAYANAZ7BROXSLPV4QD3U.jpg&h=13f6f384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方去年底高調拘捕多人，指抗爭者支援組織「星火同盟」涉洗黑錢。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方去年底高調拘捕多人，指抗爭者支援組織「星火同盟」涉洗黑錢，指控本案18歲被告洗黑錢，指他從星火相關的空殼公司收取4.8萬港元。惟洗黑錢案只聞樓梯響，最終查出被告販毒，只被落案起訴相關罪行。被告昨在區域法院承認三罪，求情透露繼父為退休警員，他為「賺快錢」而犯案。法官李慶年判刑時寄語青年「莫貪一時樂，種下未來苦」，最終判監42個月、罰款2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：官轟律政司「常陷我哋於不義」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求情指與退休警繼父同住<br />\n<br />\n被告。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告沒有案底，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。他跟着講解如何根據毒品重量量刑，向被告解釋最終刑期，指在監禁期內若行為良好，28個月後可出獄，叮囑他期間「好好珍惜，學多啲嘢，珍惜自己，最緊要錯而能改。呢段時間販毒分子不會再接觸你，喺裏面規規矩矩咁生活。記住，向毒品Say 咩呀？」被告答「Say No」。李官笑稱「你又識㗎喎」。他又拿起紙筆、贈被告十個大字：「莫貪一時樂，種下未來苦」，並寄語被告要好好對待媽媽，「呢個世界，社運好、疫情好，最緊要屋企人」。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC367/20"},{"pid":"ebcf4d0a3af2427c488c27b34577b1f46268464d","tid":2284251,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62214f9eb02d12ef8c1191ac104d8a9541690191","tid":2284251,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebcf4d0a3af2427c488c27b34577b1f46268464d","tid":2284251,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45183330163f90d7d52054eba9dc3826adb4ef4d","tid":2284251,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>求情透露繼父為退休警員</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f6a13b4ebc2305150cb86c3ad98a5ef6d2153e82","tid":2284251,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"原來又係關警察事唔關星火事<br />\n<br />\n警察真係同罪惡掛上等號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d072ba8c0dbf3f22f1d5e97bf25e9ad4d1a1c9e","tid":2284251,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"D狗又亂屈人洗黑錢"}]}